attachment:asucd06b.jpg


The ["ASUCD"] Senate contains 12 senators that manage a '''9.2 million dollar budget''' and officially do not embezzle.

As for elections, all undergraduate students at ["UC Davis" UCD] can vote for anyone they want.  In addition to independent candidates, there are "["Slate" slates]" here at ["UC Davis"] -- akin to political parties.  They are (in 2004):

 * ["Student Focus"]
 * ["L.E.A.D."] - Official [http://www.votelead.com/ website]
 * ["Friends Urging Campus Kindness"] (formerly ["SOSSS"])

For more information, see ["Senate Candidates"].


